        You Are Here:  

       Programmes  / 
	  
      Science Shack

     

 
   




	 

	


	

	

	 






	 















		 
			
		  						  



			 
					
				 


	
















						
					 

					 Seemingly impossible challenges are put to the scientific test in the ever-popular  Science Shack , presented by Adam Hart-Davis and his talented team of scientists and engineers. 



						




					 

				 

		  





	 
		 Welcome from Adam 
	 



	
















	  What's Science Shack all about anyway? Adam Hart-Davis gives us the low down on the series in his personal  welcome .  






	 
		 First series 
	 



	
















	  In the  first series  the  Science Shack  team take on a high profile wobble, a lightning strike and a future without fossil fuels.  






	 
		 Second series 
	 



	
















	  More seemingly impossible challenges are put to the scientific test as the Science Shack team return for a  second series .  




		  

		   

		 








	

	  






	 
		 					
			 Free learning 
		 



	










		 Learn something new, from natural history to ecology. There's something for everyone on our  Learning page . 
	 


		







 
	 
		 Taking it further 
	 



	
















	  Interested in science? Why not take a course with the Open University? Check out our  study page .  
 



	
	   
	
	 





	

	  






	 
		 					
			 Have your say 
		 



	










		 Science isn't for the eccentric and the mad - take the level headed approach, join others and find out how fun science can be on our  forum . 
	 


		







 
	 
		 Order your free prospectus 
	 



	
















	  Find out more about OU courses on offer and ways to study -  order your guide to courses .  
 



	
	   
	
	 





	




	



 




	


 
